se.jguru.nazgul.core.configuration.model

Interface MutableProperty<K extends Serializable & Comparable<K>,V extends Serializable>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Property<K,V>, Serializable, se.jguru.nazgul.tools.validation.api.Validatable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMutableProperty, AbstractStringKeyedMutableProperty, DateTimeProperty, IntegerProperty, StringProperty

    public interface MutableProperty<K extends Serializable & Comparable<K>,V extends Serializable>
extends Property<K,V>
    Specification for a mutable Property whose value can be updated. This specification is typically only used by administrative tooling, as opposed to applications (or other configuration clients) which should regard Properties are read-only.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
